## 📖 Scene 1: Nayi Shuruwaat — Git Kaun Hai?

Ek tha Raj — ek junior developer. Pehle din office mein ek senior developer ne socha — "Isko Git sikhana padega, nahi toh zindagi bhar headache rahega!"

Raj samjhdar tha. Usne poochha: "Git kya hota hai?"

Senior: "Bhai, Git ek **version control system** hai. Tere code ka poora history rakhta hai. Agar kuch galti ho jaaye toh wapas le sakta hai. Aur team ke sath bhi code safely share kar sakta hai!"

Raj: "Cool! Chalein, shuru karte hain!"

