## 🌳 Scene 5: Branch Ka Chakkar — `git branch`, `git checkout`, `git switch`

### Branch Kya Hota Hai?

Senior ne samjhaya: "Imagine karo — ek road hai jo do branches mein bant gaya. Main road par original code hai, aur alag branch par tu apna experiment kar sakta hai!"

### Branch Banao

Raj ne naya feature develop karna tha — login system!

```bash
# Method 1: Pehle branch banao, phir checkout karo
git branch feature/login-system
git checkout feature/login-system

# Method 2: Dono ek saath (modern way)
git checkout -b feature/login-system

# Method 3: switch (latest command)
git switch -c feature/login-system

# Saari branches dekho
git branch
git branch -a              # remote branches bhi dekho

# Local branches list
git branch -l

# Branch ka history dekho
git branch -v              # last commit ke saath

# Branch list filtering
git branch --list "feature/*"
```

### Branch Mein Kaam Karo

```bash
# Ab ye branch main hai
# Login system ka code likho
echo "function login() { }" > login.js

# Changes commit karo
git add login.js
git commit -m "feat: login system ka basic structure"

# Branch status check karo
git log --oneline
```

### Branch Se Branch Create Karo

```bash
# Current branch par hun — feature/login-system
# Iska ek sub-branch banana hai

git checkout -b feature/login-validation
# Isme validation logic likhega

git add validation.js
git commit -m "feat: email validation add kiya"

# Ab wapas main login branch par
git checkout feature/login-system
git log --oneline    # ye validation commit yaha nahi aayega
```

### Branch Rename Karo

```bash
# Current branch ka naam change karo
git branch -m feature/login-system feature/user-authentication

# Kisi aur branch ka naam change karo
git branch -m feature/login-system feature/user-auth
```

