## 🔄 Scene 6: Merge Karo Bhai — `git merge`

### Feature Complete! Ab Main Mein Merge Karna Hai

Raj ka login feature complete ho gaya. Ab use main branch mein daalna hai:

```bash
# Pehle main branch pe jao
git checkout main

# Aur merge karo
git merge feature/login-system
```

#### Case 1: Simple Merge (Fast Forward)

Agar dono branches ek line mein hain:

```
main:      C1 ——— C2
              ↓
feature:       ——— C3 ——— C4

Merge ke baad:
main:      C1 ——— C2 ——— C3 ——— C4
```

```bash
# Output aayega:
# Fast-forward
#  login.js       | 1 +
#  1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)
```

#### Case 2: Merge Conflict! 😱

Kya hoga jab dono branches mein same line par different code ho:

**Conflict scenario:**

```
main:      C1 ——— C2 (index.html: <h1>Welcome</h1>)
                ↓
feature:    ——— C3 (index.html: <h1>Login</h1>)

Git confuse ho gaya — dono mein se kaunsa code rakhe?
```

```bash
git merge feature/login-system

# Output:
# Auto-merging index.html
# CONFLICT (content): Merge conflict in index.html
# Automatic merge failed; fix conflicts and then commit the result.
```

**Conflict File Dekho:**

```bash
# Conflict dekha jayega file mein
cat index.html

# Output:
# <<<<<<< HEAD
# <h1>Welcome</h1>
# =======
# <h1>Login</h1>
# >>>>>>> feature/login-system
```

**Conflict Fix Karo:**

```bash
# File manually edit karo — VS Code editor open karo
# Ya terminal se bhi kar sakte ho
echo "<h1>Welcome to Login</h1>" > index.html

# Phir mark as resolved
git add index.html
git commit -m "fix: merge conflict resolve kiya login feature ke saath"

# Ya automatically current branch ko rakho
git merge --ours feature/login-system
git add index.html
git commit

# Ya incoming branch ko rakho
git merge --theirs feature/login-system
git add index.html
git commit
```

### Branch Delete Karo

Feature merge ho gaya, toh branch ko clean up karo:

```bash
# Local branch delete karo
git branch -d feature/login-system          # safe delete
git branch -D feature/login-system          # force delete

# Remote branch delete karo
git push origin --delete feature/login-system
git push -d origin feature/login-system     # shorthand

# Jitne bhi branches delete karne ho
git branch -d feature/login-system feature/password-reset
```

### Merge Strategies

```bash
# Simple merge (default)
git merge feature/branch

# Recursive merge (default for multiple base commits)
git merge --recursive feature/branch

# Squash all commits into one
git merge --squash feature/branch
git commit -m "feat: login system feature"

# Rebase aur merge (linear history)
git merge --rebase feature/branch

# No fast forward (always create merge commit)
git merge --no-ff feature/branch -m "Merged feature/branch into main"
```

