## 📦 Scene 11: Adhoora Kaam Save Karo — `git stash`

### Problem: Code Complete Nahi Hua, Lekin Switch Karna Padha!

Boss sudden aaya: "Raj! Main branch mein urgent bug fix karna hai!"

Raj: "Lekin mere login feature ke commits abhi half-baked hain..."

### Solution: `git stash`

```bash
# Current changes ko temporarily save karo
git stash
# Ya detailed message ke saath
git stash save "WIP: login form validation"
git stash push -m "WIP: login form validation"

# Stash list dekho
git stash list
# stash@{0}: WIP: login form validation
# stash@{1}: WIP: email verification
# stash@{2}: On feature/login-system: incomplete work

# Ab main branch pe jao aur fix karo
git checkout main
git pull
# Bug fix karo
git add .
git commit -m "fix: urgent bug in payment"
git push

# Ab feature branch pe wapas jao
git checkout feature/login-system

# Apna saved work wapas lo
git stash pop              # latest stash
git stash pop stash@{0}    # specific stash

# Ya sirf apply karo (stash baqi rahe)
git stash apply
git stash apply stash@{0}

# Stash dekho (apply nahi karte)
git stash show
git stash show stash@{0}
git stash show -p stash@{0}   # patch format

# Stash delete karo
git stash drop stash@{0}
git stash clear             # sab stash delete

# Stash se naya branch banao
git stash branch feature/from-stash
```

