## 💡 Scene 16: Advanced Tips & Tricks

### Aliases (Short Commands)

```bash
# Commands ko short banaao
git config --global alias.st status
git config --global alias.co checkout
git config --global alias.br branch
git config --global alias.ci commit
git config --global alias.unstage 'restore --staged'
git config --global alias.last 'log -1 HEAD'
git config --global alias.visual 'log --graph --oneline --all'

# Ab use karo
git st           # instead of git status
git co main      # instead of git checkout main
git visual       # beautiful history
```

### Git Hooks (Automatic Actions)

```bash
# .git/hooks folder mein files add karo

# Pre-commit hook (commit se pehle)
# .git/hooks/pre-commit

#!/bin/bash
# Run tests before commit
npm test
if [ $? -ne 0 ]; then
  echo "Tests failed!"
  exit 1
fi

# Executable banao
chmod +x .git/hooks/pre-commit
```

### Ignore Files (`.gitignore`)

```bash
# Root directory mein .gitignore file banao
echo "node_modules/" > .gitignore
echo "*.log" >> .gitignore
echo ".env" >> .gitignore
echo "dist/" >> .gitignore

# Ya .gitignore templates online dekho
# GitHub pe sab language ke templates hain
```

### Search Karo (`git grep`)

```bash
# Repository mein search karo
git grep "TODO"
git grep "function login"
git grep -n "error handling"    # line numbers

# Specific branch mein
git grep "console.log" main
```

### Bisect (Bug Ka Culprit Find Karo)

```bash
# Bug ka commit dhundho
git bisect start
git bisect bad HEAD         # current bad hai
git bisect good v1.0        # pehle ka version good tha

# Git binary search karega
# Test karo current state ko
# Agar bad hai
git bisect bad
# Agar good hai
git bisect good

# Repeat...
# Jab culprit mil jaye
git bisect reset
```

