## 🎓 Scene 17: Team Collaboration — Best Practices

### PR (Pull Request) Culture

```bash
# Feature branch banao
git checkout -b feature/new-feature

# Work karo, commits karo
git add .
git commit -m "feat: new feature implementation"

# Push karo
git push origin feature/new-feature

# GitHub par PR banao
# Apni team ke liye description likho
# Code review request karo

# Reviewer ne comments diye? Update karo
git add .
git commit -m "fix: address review comments"
git push origin feature/new-feature

# PR automatically update

# Approved! Ab merge karo
# GitHub "Squash and Merge" or "Merge" option use karo
```

### Commit Message Convention

```
<type>(<scope>): <subject>
<BLANK LINE>
<body>
<BLANK LINE>
<footer>

Examples:
feat(auth): add login functionality
fix(navbar): responsive menu not working
docs(README): update installation steps
style(button): align CSS classes
refactor(api): simplify error handling
test(login): add unit tests for login page
chore(deps): update dependencies

