## 🆘 Scene 18: Common Problems & Solutions

### Problem 1: "Detached HEAD" State

```bash
# Ye warning dikhaata hai
# HEAD is now at a1b2c3d

# Solution: Wapas branch par jao
git checkout main
# Ya naya branch banao
git checkout -b recovery-branch
```

### Problem 2: "Everything up-to-date" (Lekin Main Branch Update Nahi Hua)

```bash
# Asliyat: push hua hai, lekin branch default nahi
# GitHub settings check karo

# Local update karo
git pull origin main
```

### Problem 3: SSH vs HTTPS Clone Issues

```bash
# HTTPS (easier, par har baar password)
git clone https://github.com/user/repo.git

# SSH (one-time setup, phir password nahi)
git clone git@github.com:user/repo.git

# SSH key generate karo (first time)
ssh-keygen -t ed25519 -C "your-email@example.com"
# Public key GitHub mein add karo
```

### Problem 4: Large File Commit

```bash
# Accidentally large file commit kar di?
git rm --cached large-file.zip
git commit -m "remove large file"

# .gitignore mein add karo
echo "large-file.zip" >> .gitignore
```

